| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1583 — Recovery Inhibition (hunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ea8c7791-5f58-56ec-95e3-429bc0a0d738"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
